description: Numbers that are the sum of at most 4 nonzero 4th powers.
links: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n=1..1000
prog: (PARI) N=1000; x='x+O('x^N); /* terms up to N-1 */S=ceil(N^(1/4));v=Vec(sum(k=-S,S,x^(k^4))^4);for(n=1,#v,if(v[n]!=0,print1(n-1,", "))); /* Joerg Arndt, Jun 25 2011 */
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_
